node.text: In celebration of my @Bet Her Award Nomination for my song #Rooted featuring @EsterDean, I want to Celebrate MY FANS. It was so much fun having some of you in this Viral clip I did with @Thomeography and @Jamaicacraft and some incredible dancers! My Melanin Queens, My Black Queens, All Queens shining! You brought your babies and all! This truly warmed my heart.. I did my part just 2 weeks after giving birth.. I was pushing and having fun! It’s All Rooted in Me. Rooted in You. Rooted in Us! Keep on Dancin’ #StayRooted #Dance

node.text:
Working with the Legendary photographer @DavidYarrow has always been a dream come true for @DangeRussWilson and I as we have dreamed about partnering together to make a difference in the world with him. Going on this journey with David was truly special to us as we have his book and photography around the house. David is not only the world’s best at captioning iconic moments, but he has the heart of a lion. He believes we can all make the world a better place by joining forces. 

When we connected on this vision, we realized for this shoot we wanted to do a throwback to one of his iconic moments of the past, but with a twist. A twist representing diversity and inclusion. A twist of new age modern…present, and past. David said, “Lets go to Montana where I can build a vignette that lives and breaths cinema whilst playing on the absence of cultural refinement in the Wild West. I want to take you to my favorite location to shoot in the world -  the legendary Pioneer Bar - high up in the mountains of West Montana.”

Together, our mission was not only to celebrate the diversity of America and remind us of the importance of inclusivity, but to also demonstrate that cultural differences led with Love, Respect, & Care can help us all grow to be a better version of America and ourselves. 

In this journey of making the world a better place, we hope to raise funds for the youth through our @WhyNotYouFdn and David Yarrow’s foundation. Join us as we celebrate love. Photos release works wide starting next week!

node.text:
A whole year of fun on @WW! When I started WW to help me navigate my health journey postpartum, I picked it because IT WORKS. I’d seen it work for so many friends so I got started #wwambassador. While I knew it worked, I quickly learned that the program was way more than I expected. A few things that quickly became my favorite things about the program: 
⭐️ They have over 2000 Coaches to help you along the way to your goals and they’re there 24/7 if you need. Shoutout to my coach @i.am.pierce for supporting me! 
⭐️ Wellness that works & weight loss that works. WW helps with holistic wellness and has got you covered for food, fitness, mindset and sleep! You can reflect on your progress every week & set new goals. I personally love the tips & tools around positive mindset.
⭐️ The dub dub club is huge & so supportive! I’ve gotten so many great messages from my WW fam and millions of people have had success!  
⭐️ The app is amazing!! It has 1.5M+ 5 star reviews. Add another one from me!   

I have a special offer for my fam here if you’re interested in trying it out. Use my code CIARA for $10 off a membership at ww.com!!*
